                Vala Saturio<lb break="no" n="2"/>nis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XX <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ita</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iliae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>17 aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes noch der untere Teil einer frontal sitzenden weiblichen Figur. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. (B): Kubitschek: Z. 3: fi(liae).</p>
            </div>
